  "narrative": "DRIVER\nUSD leads D1+H4 CSM at 100 with VIX up 6.78%, S&P 500 down 1.24%, and copper collapsing 4.15% confirming risk-off regime as the dominant macro force. USDJPY long is the cleanest expression with D1+H4 Buy and H4 momentum at 79, while USDCAD long amplifies via USD strength with CAD the H4 CSM accelerator divergence pair. AUD H4 CSM fading hard to 26 from D1 at 65 is the most important short-term signal \u2014 AUDUSD sells confirmed by AUDJPY correlation at 0.90 dragging both pairs lower simultaneously.\n\nMOMENTUM\nGaining: USDCAD CMP 60, D1 59 rising sharply, H4 70 confirming upside on both timeframes\nFading: EURUSD CMP 37 H4 13 collapsing, GBPUSD CMP 36 H4 13 decelerating, NZDUSD CMP 43 H4 17 dropping hard\n\nWATCH\nUS 10Y yield extending above 4.60 triggers USDJPY acceleration toward next resistance as carry demand reinforces USD bid\nSilver breaking below current levels extends AUDUSD downside as commodity currency correlation intensifies the AUD fade signal\nCopper holding below 6.30 confirms USDCAD upside continuation with CAD unable to recover H4 CSM momentum",
